en.name: AR-15 DURAMAG SS 7.62x39 28-round magazine
en.description: The 7.62x39 DURAMAG SS magazines are the ultimate choice for running this caliber in any AR15 style firearm. Feeding tapered cases like the 7.62x39mm into the straight magazine well of the AR platform has never been easy. Until DURAMAG™, many thought the combination was simply not possible to produce reliably. Thanks to extensive quality control built into their designs, every magazine is sure to run flawlessly. With DURAMAG SS, now you can finally enjoy the close-in power of 7.62x39mm reliably in your AR platform.

en.name: AR-15 USGI 5.56x45 20-round magazine
en.description: This AR-15 USGI 5.56x45mm 20-round magazine is a durable, military-grade mag designed for reliability and performance. Made from lightweight aluminum with a hard-anodized finish, it features a stainless steel spring and anti-tilt follower for smooth, consistent feeding. Compact and ideal for bench shooting or prone positions, it's a dependable choice for any AR-platform rifle chambered in 5.56 NATO or .223 Remington.

en.name: AR-15 USGI Vintage 5.56x45 20-round magazine
en.description: A Vintage USGI 5.56x45 20-round magazine, manufactured around the time of the Vietnam War. These mags were often loaded with only 18-rounds to avoid spring fatigue and weapon jamming, as such it is not recommended to load above 18 rounds into this specific magazine.
